ail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa7KeuxB.jpg&h=6eb7f2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/95FtyZg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F95FtyZg.jpg&h=ecc3ae69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/caConSC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcaConSC.jpg&h=d1559671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o12zBzL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo12zBzL.jpg&h=30775035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1cca6cdf5b54fe789e829a9fcfd04925f80b767e","tid":1477710,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:39:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0mPBYVF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0mPBYVF.jpg&h=ae53ee7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n幫推&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">觀音廟導賞圖</span><br />\n馬頭圍道上路<br />\n土瓜灣道下路<br />\n1. 土瓜灣絕非方便上落地點，冇地鐵，居民極藍，大量同鄉會阻礙旅遊，不過所有旅行團聚餐同藥房集中係土瓜灣近海果邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 紅磡警署唔係紅磡，紅磡果個係交通警黎<br />\n東九龍走廊極危險，隨時無啦啦有一大堆警察增援亂咁打人，天光道同佛光街天橋都一樣，大家都知而家警察好危險啦<br />\n<br />\n黃埔除左有黃埔站，向上路可以出旺角/尖咀/過海<br />\n下路可以出尖咀，最緊要海濱有跑道可出星光大道<br />\n記得千祈唔好<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">817</span></span>&nbsp;黎參觀觀音廟啊"},{"pid":"3b72fd6fe09a3fa6d487fb1bda1a17ee99b9edd2","tid":1477710,"uid":292893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T08:49:14.000Z","msg":"816㩒錢 816遮打見 818維園見"},{"pid":"b1bcb9cf22312dd4569706944d8057aad6ac97c3","tid":1477710,"uid":1134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcaff2ab21a12233f122ec8d1b9ee2f5bee47772","tid":